{"tid":690594,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【七年之癢？】與YoYo婚姻亮紅燈 王浩信稱「接受好同壞嘅情況」","createTime":"2018-06-05T04:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-05T15:39:22.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa32c58881bc8b31158dafe8055ada8b5a64fa6","tid":690594,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T04:07:52.000Z","msg":"早前傳王浩信同YoYo(陳自瑤)捱唔過「七年之癢」，又有指王浩信日前承諾買獨立屋俾老婆，點知轉頭就以3306.6萬元購入清水灣傲瀧11座高層B單位送俾媽咪，事前老婆YoYo毫不知情，令YoYo死心，主動提出離婚，無論愛跟被愛係唔係真係冇自由，感動過係唔係真係更難受?<br />\n<br />\n今日有周刊指王浩信近年信基督教，開始學識放下，明白要活在當下，面對愛情，佢會接受好同壞嘅情況，佢喺報道中強調婚姻關係冇任何改變，以後唔會再多講，佢認為婚姻係會有困境，要學習同汲取教訓，認為珍惜身邊本來擁有嘅嘢已經好快樂，因為係無價。未知佢口中嘅「無價」係唔係講緊YoYo呢!?<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/05/120729_3171ad88f1704c4367cb172d07351f52.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F05%2F120729_3171ad88f1704c4367cb172d07351f52.png&h=bb93f5e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180605/58279212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180605%2F58279212&d=AZAWpLf1Nx5nkV5bLvirGsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=8da4ab55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180605%2F58279212&h=50c30ff8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180605/58279212</a>"},{"pid":"50252bc767b227a88fd9058e97b1809935e2d9dd","tid":690594,"uid":11809,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-05T04:50:04.000Z","msg":"呢條擺明係大滾友啦<br />\n<br />\n之前霉到仆街冇人埋<br />\n<br />\n依家上咗位梗係要大玩特玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"434b174f062c9546f1937789b8bb000f92eb0f42","tid":690594,"uid":152726,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy